name: The Cosmic Gaze
description: 4K Size. Made in 2021 by Toxic Motel & Pemuda Sinarmas. "Tatapan Kosmos" in English means "The Cosmic Gaze". We are all one in this universe. So when we look at another things or persons, we are actually blends to each other, since we are all comin' from one big bang, or Universal God.
